data.description: Welcome Home! Ideal 4 bedroom, 2.5 Azle home nestled in on 4.5 treed acres with barn, chicken coop, and plenty of workshop space! You will appreciate the wrap around porch and the curb appeal of this home. The large living room with a stately fireplaces sits at the heart of the home! The eat-in kitchen offers a breakfast bar, built-in stainless steel appliances, lots of storage and prep space, a walk-in pantry, and a bright breakfast nook! Downstairs primary suite with dual sinks, separate shower, soaking tub, and walk-in closet. Spacious secondary bedrooms and bath share the second floor. The 4th bedroom can be used as a comfortable home office or a cozy den. Excellent location just minutes from Eagle Mountain like. Picture yourself relaxing under the big Texas sky surrounded by the sights and sounds of local wildlife! Don't miss the workshop with electricity. Easy access to major roads, dining and shopping options. 3D tour is available online!
